<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
      <h1 class="cover-heading">About Me!</h1>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <%= image_tag "Learn_Nov_2018_Eric2.jpg", alt: "profile image" %>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <p class="lead">Hello my name is Eric Uyemura!  I began coding in June of 2018. Ever since I made my first HTML page I've been addicted to learning more and more. My passion is in full stack development, I especially love Rails and React, but am constantly trying to learn new languages, frameworks, and libraries.  I also love typing furiously into the terminal and feeling like an operator in the Matrix.</p>
          <p class="lead">One of my favorite books is, "Zen Mind Beginner's Mind", by Shunryu Suzuki, it advises to always take the mindset of a beginner, to never be above learning more.  This is easy for me as a beginner, but I plan on taking this attitude with me in all avenues of life.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lead--buttons">
          <p class="lead lead--button">
            <%= link_to "Contact Me", contact_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-secondary" %>
          </p>
          <p class="lead lead--button">
            <%= link_to fa_icon("file-pdf-o", text: "My Resume", right: true), '/EUResumePort.doc.pdf', class: "btn btn-lg btn-secondary header-text", target: '_blank' %>
          </p>
          <p class="lead lead--button">
            <%= link_to fa_icon("file-pdf-o", text: "Vizisites Recommendation, right: true), '/recommendation.pdf', class: "btn btn-lg btn-secondary header-text", target: '_blank' %>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Skills</h1>
    <div class="skills">
      <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
      <div class="skill">
        <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
        <div class="progress">
          <div
          class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
          role="progressbar"
          aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
          aria-valuemax="100"
          style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
          ></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
